@Evan-Gao : Is it possible that you're not using the latest versions of the tutorial files (from https://github.com/tensorflow/models/tree/master/tutorials/image/cifar10)? Or perhaps there are some stale files in `/tmp/cifar10_train` (the [default directory](https://github.com/tensorflow/models/blob/master/tutorials/image/cifar10/cifar10_train.py#L48) where the tutorial places it files).

